These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
City: venice, new-york, marseilles, edinburgh, rome, colone, london
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is the argentine##1
 8. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person traveling to london is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| City           | rome | edinburgh | new-york | marseilles | venice | colone | london |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

