.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
City: miami, hannover, hamburg, nizza, edinburgh, liverpool, new-york
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is in the middle##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| City   | hannover      | hamburg   | nizza   | edinburgh      | miami       | new-york       | liverpool     |

