.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
7 different games are played: go, snooker, mah-jongg, backgammon, domino, canasta, whist
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 2. the person playing domino is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 4. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the bartender is the person playing domino##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the person playing canasta is the photographer##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the person playing whist is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Game   | snooker | domino     | mah-jongg  | canasta       | go       | whist  | backgammon   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

