.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, milk, mirinda, cola, tea, iced-tea
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person drinking cola is the australian##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person drinking milk is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the thai is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | tea    | iced-tea     | mirinda     | milk      | sprite | cola      | fanta     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

