.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, drawing, gardening, magic-tricks, sudoku, video-games
There are 7 different favourite colors: brown, light-blue, apricot, yellow, white, purple, blue
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who likes blue##1
 2. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 5. the person who likes white is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who likes white##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | sudoku     | gardening | video-games | magic-tricks | board-games |
| Color     | blue   | apricot    | white | purple     | brown         | yellow     | light-blue        |

