The people prefer 7 different types of sport: surfing, ice-hockey, badminton, golfing, golf, swimming, climbing
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is golfing##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | coffee | soy-milk   | 7up | iced-tea | sprite  | juice | almond-milk |
| Sport   | golfing   | golf | surfing | swimming     | ice-hockey | climbing | badminton   |

