.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-10::.
There 7 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, orange, potato, pumpkin, strawberry, watermelon
7 different pets are kept: pony, guinea-pig, ferret, rabbit, dog, mouse, bird
 1. the person eating potato is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 4. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 8. the person eating strawberry is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
10. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
| Food   | pumpkin    | orange    | kiwi   | strawberry | grapefruit | watermelon | potato   |
| Pet    | ferret | dog | bird | mouse  | pony       | rabbit     | guinea-pig |

