 7. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 8. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 9. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
11. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
